flowchart TD
    M([Component mounted]) --> S[Setup runs<br/>useState/ref/$state init]
    S --> E[Effect runs<br/>useEffect / onMounted / $effect]
    E --> A[Component active]
    A -->|Reactive read changes<br/>or re-render triggered| C1[Cleanup runs<br/>return fn from effect]
    C1 --> E
    A --> U([Component unmounted])
    E --> C2[Final cleanup runs<br/>onUnmounted / cleanup return]
    C2 --> U

    style M fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#1e40af,color:#0f172a
    style U fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#991b1b,color:#0f172a
    style S fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#854d0e,color:#0f172a
    style E fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#854d0e,color:#0f172a
    style A fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#166534,color:#0f172a
    style C1 fill:#fae8ff,stroke:#86198f,color:#0f172a
    style C2 fill:#fae8ff,stroke:#86198f,color:#0f172a
